Package: MadingleyR
Type: Package
Title: MadingleyR: General Ecosystem Model
Version: 1.0.4
Author: Selwyn Hoeks
Maintainer: The package maintainer <s.hoeks@science.ru.nl>
Description: The MadingleyR package is a wrapper around the C++ code of the Madingley model. It was intended as an accessible and transparent tool to lower the barrier of using the Madingley model, thereby broadening the Madingley comminity. 
